title: Evergreen High School football player died after being injured in game Friday night
text:
Evergreen High School football player died after being injured i - SWX Right Now-Sports for Spokane, CdA, Tri-Cities, WA Member Center: Evergreen High School football player died after being injured in game Friday night Harboview Medical Center confirmed Monday high school football player Kenny Bui died SEATTLE - 
Harborview Medical Center in Seattle has confirmed the Evergreen High School football player who was injured in a game last Friday has died. 
Kenny Bui was injured in the 4th quarter of a game against Highline when he took a hard hit. Bui, a senior, was taken to Harboview's Intensive Care Unit and it was announced Monday he had passed away.
